WEBVTT

00:13:29.290 --> 00:13:30.971
And that night in Princeton,

00:13:30.995 --> 00:13:35.296
a certain gap in the chain of arguments
was driving me crazy.

00:13:35.658 --> 00:13:40.251
I was putting in there all my energy
and experience and tricks,

00:13:40.275 --> 00:13:42.017
and still nothing was working.

00:13:42.553 --> 00:13:46.435
1 a.m., 2 a.m., 3 a.m.,

00:13:46.459 --> 00:13:47.767
not working.

00:13:48.545 --> 00:13:52.866
Around 4 a.m., I go to bed in low spirits.

00:13:53.915 --> 00:13:56.375
Then a few hours later,

00:13:56.399 --> 00:13:57.550
waking up and go,

00:13:57.574 --> 00:14:00.931
"Ah, it's time to get
the kids to school --"